N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4051.3 - When hunts committee may permit start

State Regulations

At meetings under the jurisdiction of the hunts
committee, the hunts committee may permit horses to start in cases in which
such horse's certificates of registration are not on file at the identification
office. Notes
